Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She blocked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of mobile suit is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,GUND-ARM...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no match for Its individual Permet code,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's one machine that's similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochs Earth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the Witch's mobile suit, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your groom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My lousy father\Ndecided without consulting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to marry whoever the Holder is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is to go to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They build mobile suits like this at Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease dueling immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease dueling immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The front management company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Student ID Number LP041.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your mobile suit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are to be taken into custody\Non suspicion of using a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong! This is Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to manage the fronts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules set by the President\Ntake precedence over all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The President?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That lousy father of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't all the Gundam types disposed of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly doesn't\Nlook like an old machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't those things take\Nthe lives of their pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that girl is alive, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury. Age 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Student ID Number LP041.\NPiloting department...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is deceased
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and your mother\Nis currently assigned to Lagrange 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I already answered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you acknowledge that\Nthe machine you were piloting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that the use of machines\Nequipped with the GUND Format
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has been frozen and prohibited\Nby the Agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not a member of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Vanadis Institute\Nthat developed the Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Gundam pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look like a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Any links to Vanadis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mobile suit is registered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Shin Sei Development\NCorporation of Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still investigating--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's not a witch,\Nthen how do you explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a bunch of miners\Nat Mercury could build their own Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the ghost of Ochs Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel results are void.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Confiscate that machine immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and send the pilot back to Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then your son will reclaim\Nthe title of Holder, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summon Shin Sei's representative.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will hold an inquiry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel results were voided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she cheated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew something wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably still interrogating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel sorry for that Mercurian girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she made off\Nwith someone else's prize, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanaura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This arrived\Nfrom the front management company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That transfer student took yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I offered it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The lending of student notebooks\Nis against school regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that girl be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An Earthian like you should stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just concentrate on your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the Dueling Committee for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You work awfully hard for a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch trial at the head office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she really be a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious about someone besides yourself, Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love is something I'll never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your great "ace"\Nwho broke these, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my brother told me to fix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he's sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably got summoned\Nafter losing that duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,By his father, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better than a parent\Nwho's aloof from their child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You just leave that transfer student\Ndangling after she fought for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked her to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell her when she gets back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not to meddle in others' affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you don't seem to know,\Nwe'll fill you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mercurian girl is going to be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to scrap her mobile suit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard my dad say so--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? You got a prob--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,FIx it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch my tomatoes, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. Shin Sei Development Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Founded 33 years ago.\NRanked D within the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,151st place in sales?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the bottom of the ladder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed she got into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They made their own mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But unless it's approved, what good is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had a bigger supporter,\Nit might've been a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At our school, you're as good as the rank\Nof the company that recommended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly be proud of being born on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Spacians who are holding us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down, Chuchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if they hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our usual table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We just finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done eating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw that out with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Learn some manners, Spacian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Chuchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nika, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I said, there's a possibility\Nthat was a forbidden machine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only asking to see the pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not up to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's it up to, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}President Delling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, if you would please leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To prevent an infectious spread of "SV29"\Nconfirmed in Front Autonomous Sector 33...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go back to class," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I have a message from your father
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll read it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Miorine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unenrolling you from the school."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll arrange a groom myself.\NReturn immediately."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who decided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that my fiance would be\Nselected through duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta's the one who won the duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No man chosen by that jerk\Nwill be a husband of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use saying that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He never consults me, he never explains...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's enrolling me at this school
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or forcing me to quit piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or deciding who I should be friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my own mother's funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Mistress Miorine out of your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, die, die, die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Ms. Miorine Rembran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Designated Colony Coordinate XY72Z53.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the rendezvous point for my escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to finally meet you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't show up\Nto meet us the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of after-sales care?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You did pay us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't changed your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to escape now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we act now, I can send you\Nto Earth as you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can wait for 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a decision you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really this easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky the spaceport controller\Nwas a collaborator of ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you and I happened to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be leaving the airspace\Ncontrolled by this port in 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we do, we can't change our course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress Miorine has disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the men watching her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She shook them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we seal the port?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the immigration authorities\Nspread a dragnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's bound for Earth, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nwhen will the inquiry begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just confirmed the arrival\Nof the Shin Sei representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So a member of the Jeturk family\Nlost a duel in a Jeturk mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to destroy\Nthe company's reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around, I'll arrange\Nto have the duel result voided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't embarrass me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The representative of\Nthe Shin Sei Development Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other for 3 years\Nsince your appointment as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Prospera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to talk to the President\Non your behalf, the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. The opposite, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you who should ask me for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Elan Ceres.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, I'm a student at Asticassia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The guard here let me do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's so nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to learn more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Prospera, representative of\Nthe Shin Sei Development Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have ties to the Vanadis Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did you build a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aerial is not a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a product of Shin Sei's\Nnewly developed drone technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say drone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddiq.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,During the duel, that machine's\NPermet influx values exceeded the standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a unique characteristic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the GUND Format,\Nthe core system of all Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If that machine is equipped\Nwith the GUND Format,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you should also have detected a data storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There was none detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Its control system is based on\Na conventional Permet link.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident that it complies with all\Nof the group's technology provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone doesn't prove it isn't a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove that it is, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Prospera...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are merely using the lack\Nof evidence as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell us\Nthat black is white?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're one of the smallest, but\Nstill a member of the Benerit Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are, of course,\Naware of the Cathedra Agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help doubting\Nwhen you come dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the face behind this mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,were both claimed\Nby Mercury's magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Environmental conditions\Non Mercury are severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, utilizing our drone technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to mine for Permet\Nwithout putting anyone in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to continue\Nthe Aerial's development.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in need of the group's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That thing is a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit shall be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get rid of the student pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to give you a piece of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you made these rules yourself,\Nyou shouldn't change them after the fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You hypocritical loser of a father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to take her to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to honor my customers' requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it comes\Nto the President's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't hurt to be owed a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As calculating as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Space is in need of new rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people\Npermitted to stand in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are the powers-that-be from the\Ntop companies of the Benerit Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are merely a student\Nwith no authority to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You look down and control my life\Nwithout asking or explaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither consultation\Nnor explanation are necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could speak out\Nagainst me because you're my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am vested with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The powerless shut their mouths and obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the rules of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move forward, you gain two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I challenge you to a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we win,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll accept Suletta as my fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose, you can do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you unable to comprehend my words?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that I'll fight\Naccording to your rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At least take responsibility\Nfor your own decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an adult, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,May I speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if was accidentally, that machine\Ndefeated our company's Dilanza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should give it time\Nto see what it can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, mobile suits from\Nother companies have made market gains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That machine could be\Nthe key to recovering our market share.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the school duels will be\Nan effective test of the Aerial's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And will you provide us with\Nthe machine's technical data?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to violate\Nthe Cathedra Agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I object!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you announce this\Nto the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about ethics!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it. The duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, Aerial will be scrapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Permet link established.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Decision Making Extension AI\Nhas been connected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Confirming deployment\Nof combat space network.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever you're ready.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Mobile Suit Gundam:\NThe Witch from Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Guel's Pride".
